title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1990-09-20
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Althea, It's All Over Now, Ramble On Rose, El Paso, Brown Eyed Women, Greatest Story Ever Told-> U.S. Blues

Set 2

Truckin', China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter, Drums-> Jam-> Dark Star-> Playin' In The Band Reprise-> Dark Star-> Jam-> Throwing Stones-> Touch Of Gray, E: Turn On Your Love Light

reviews.review_text: My Birthday Show hey now i flew from phoenix to nyc for this show my 26th b day oh boy what a high energy show this was the first tour the boys did after returning from europe with vinnie and hornsby nice mixed set list us bluz to end 1st set and the energy between garcia and hornsby was amazing second set DARK STAR 30 minutes with the playin jam in the middle a very hot show for the new line up following brents death RIP peace out SPIKE
